-- Abengoa to Develop Ethanol Plant For Brazil Development Bank
-- B y   B e n   S i l l s
-- 2012-01-12T09:41:45Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-12/abengoa-to-develop-ethanol-plant-for-brazil-development-bank.html
Abengoa SA (ABG)  will develop a second-
generation ethanol plant for  Brazil ’s National Development Bank
that uses stalks and husks from sugar cane, the company said in
an e-mailed press release. It didn’t say how much the project is
worth.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
